<h2>How to buy it?</h2>
<p>4Sight is not sold as a software product at this time, it is part of a 'total solution'. Digitalfire will work will you to make it do what you want. 
<a href="../services/contact.php">Contact</a> us, let's begin the process and talk about pricing. We will guide you on 
every step of the way. </p>

<h2>Starting Lab Data Management Now</h2>
You can download the 4Sight for DOS application from the download page if you have a Level 2 INSIGHT key. 
We can help you get started setting up procedures for your testing and compiling data now. 
Then we can migrate you to 4Sight Server later.<br><br>



